        <h2>In the USA missions section, you can find a button called "Edit". This button will create a space where you can Edit the information about the mission that you selected. The Edit section includes four things Mission name, the time period, the Team leader's name and a description of the mission. In this section, you are not required to fill out all four categories of the information you can just edit the one that you wanted to edit. Once you are happy with your information you can click on the green button called 'Submit the information and your information will display on the main page of the section.</h2>
